---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title='Privacy Policy — ADHD Flow Lab'>
  <article class='post'>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class='post-date'>Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <div class='post-content'>
      <p>ADHD Flow Lab ("we", "us") operates the website adhd-blog-kappa.vercel.app and related content channels. This policy explains how we handle information.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect minimal data. If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address (processed by our newsletter provider, beehiiv). We use standard, privacy-respecting analytics to understand aggregate traffic. We do not sell personal information.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use third-party platforms including beehiiv (email), Vercel (hosting), Pinterest, YouTube, and Etsy. When you click links to these platforms, their respective privacy policies apply. Some links are affiliate links; we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies and may use analytics cookies to improve the site. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time using the link in any email. To request deletion of any data we hold about you, contact us.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Reach out via our newsletter reply or the contact options on our channels.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
